* logging
  * in peinit
    * currently these written on the console and go through hvc0
    * they get collected by the cloud-hypervisor  --console file=blah
    * when run by a webserver, we want these to go _____
  * in perunner
    * currently these are just written to stdout

* perunner worker pool
  * spin up N workers
  * accept jobs from a queue
  * put finished jobs on a queue

* webserver
  * accept requests
  * lookup container id -> image config
  * create packed input file of peinit::Config + pearchive
  * put into worker pool (with id for connection)
  * take from result queue and send these back
